# Enterprise Resource Planning Application UI for a College [ DAIT ]
 This one is a UI/UX Design project which has enabling the efficiency to manage the records of the college students and Faculties.
 It establish interactions between Students,Parents and Faculties.With access rights assigned to Student's parents , they can easily track the records of their son/daughter.For Example :The Parent will be notified about every activity of their son/daughter through this Application.
 In this project,I have created meticulous designs to ease the navigation towards entire screens.

