## About the Project
**Type :**  [ Mobile App ]
**Purpose :** To Design a ERP more accessible , easily navigatable.
ERP in a college is used to manage and streamline all the academic, administrative, and financial activities of the institution in a single system.
To track records of academic performance and schedules , to reach every student and their parents specifically , this system helps. With Instant updates and notifications ,one can be aware of the current work progress.

With ERP, a college can:

Track student progress and attendance easily.

Manage exams & results without errors.

Collect and track fees efficiently.

Provide online portals for students and staff.
**Tools :** Figma , Canva
